70	tables	loom_views.v_line_a_equipment_status	loom_views.v_line_a_equipment_status  (view)	Saved view · 3 rows	# loom_views.v_line_a_equipment_status\n\n<!-- provenance: schema -->\nThis is a **view** created by Loom. 3 rows as of 2026-05-19.\n\n<!-- provenance: claude, 2026-05-19 -->\n## What this view represents\nShows all equipment installed on LINE-A with maintenance status and recent production activity\n\n## Definition\n\n```sql\nSELECT \n  e.equipment_id,\n  e.name as machine_name,\n  e.manufacturer,\n  e.installed_at,\n  e.last_maintenance_at,\n  e.next_maintenance_due,\n  -- Check if maintenance is due soon (within 30 days)\n  CASE \n    WHEN e.next_maintenance_due <= CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '30 days' THEN 'Maintenance due soon'\n    ELSE 'Maintenance up to date'\n  END as maintenance_status,\n  -- Get most recent production run for this line\n  (\n    SELECT MAX(pr.started_at)\n    FROM public.production_runs pr\n    WHERE pr.line_id = e.line_id\n  ) as last_production_run_on_line,\n  -- Count of production runs on this line\n  (\n    SELECT COUNT(*)\n    FROM public.production_runs pr\n    WHERE pr.line_id = e.line_id\n  ) as total_runs_on_line\nFROM public.equipment e\nWHERE e.line_id = 'LINE-A'\nORDER BY e.name\n```\n\n<!-- provenance: schema -->\n## Columns\n\n| Column | Type |\n| --- | --- |\n| `equipment_id` | integer |\n| `machine_name` | text |\n| `manufacturer` | text |\n| `installed_at` | date |\n| `last_maintenance_at` | timestamp with time zone |\n| `next_maintenance_due` | timestamp with time zone |\n| `maintenance_status` | text |\n| `last_production_run_on_line` | timestamp with time zone |\n| `total_runs_on_line` | bigint |\n\n	{"name": "v_line_a_equipment_status", "schema": "loom_views", "is_view": true, "table_id": 2286}	336ca385e0a3e463f01225f99fea25d3	ready	2026-05-20 08:54:07.905536+00	2026-05-20 08:54:07.905536+00	2026-05-20 08:54:07.905536+00	2026-05-20 08:54:07.905536+00	\N	source	\N	\N	\N
