45	tables	loom_views.v_equipment_deviation_analysis_30d	loom_views.v_equipment_deviation_analysis_30d  (view)	Saved view · 10 rows	# loom_views.v_equipment_deviation_analysis_30d\n\n<!-- provenance: schema -->\nThis is a **view** created by Loom. 10 rows as of 2026-05-18.\n\n<!-- provenance: claude, 2026-05-18 -->\n## What this view represents\n_No description provided._\n\n## Definition\n\n```sql\nSELECT \n  e.line_id,\n  e.name,\n  e.manufacturer,\n  e.installed_at,\n  e.last_maintenance_at,\n  e.next_maintenance_due,\n  COUNT(d.deviation_id) as total_deviations,\n  COUNT(d.deviation_id) FILTER (WHERE d.actual_value <> d.expected_value) as mismatch_deviations,\n  COUNT(d.deviation_id) FILTER (WHERE d.actual_value <> d.expected_value)::float / NULLIF(COUNT(d.deviation_id), 0) as mismatch_rate,\n  STRING_AGG(DISTINCT d.category, ', ' ORDER BY d.category) as categories,\n  STRING_AGG(DISTINCT d.severity, ', ' ORDER BY d.severity) as severities\nFROM public.equipment e\nLEFT JOIN public.deviations d ON e.equipment_id = d.equipment_id\n  AND d.observed_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'\nGROUP BY e.equipment_id, e.name, e.manufacturer, e.installed_at, e.last_maintenance_at, e.next_maintenance_due, e.line_id\nORDER BY mismatch_rate DESC NULLS LAST, total_deviations DESC\n```\n\n<!-- provenance: schema -->\n## Columns\n\n| Column | Type |\n| --- | --- |\n| `line_id` | text |\n| `name` | text |\n| `manufacturer` | text |\n| `installed_at` | date |\n| `last_maintenance_at` | timestamp with time zone |\n| `next_maintenance_due` | timestamp with time zone |\n| `total_deviations` | bigint |\n| `mismatch_deviations` | bigint |\n| `mismatch_rate` | double precision |\n| `categories` | text |\n| `severities` | text |\n\n	{"name": "v_equipment_deviation_analysis_30d", "schema": "loom_views", "is_view": true, "table_id": 2129}	113d126eb0de1749d937d633faeb13d4	ready	2026-05-18 06:19:21.674625+00	2026-05-20 08:54:07.898178+00	2026-05-18 06:19:21.674625+00	2026-05-18 06:19:21.674625+00