59	code	admiralpharma-tests	admiral_pharma / tests	This module contains unit tests for the admiral R package, which provides tools for clinical trial data analysis in pharmaceutical settings. The tests verify that core functions like `derive_vars_dt`,	## What this module does\nThis module contains unit tests for the admiral R package, which provides tools for clinical trial data analysis in pharmaceutical settings. The tests verify that core functions like `derive_vars_dt`, `compute_age_years`, and `create_query_data` handle edge cases correctly and throw appropriate errors for invalid inputs.\n\n## Public surface\n- `testthat` test files (e.g., `test-call_derivation.R`, `test-compute_age_years.R`)\n- Snapshot files (`_snaps/`) capturing expected error messages and outputs\n\n## Dependencies & data\n- `testthat` for unit testing framework\n- `rlang` for error handling\n- Internal admiral functions and options (e.g., `get_admiral_option`, `derive_vars_dt`)\n- Clinical trial data structures (e.g., subject keys, date variables)\n\n## When to reference\n- When adding new tests to ensure they follow admiral's error messaging conventions\n- When debugging failing tests to compare actual vs. expected outputs\n- When updating function behavior to verify error conditions remain correctly handled	{"files": ["tests/testthat/AGENTS.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/admiral_options.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/call_derivation.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/call_user_fun.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/compute_age_years.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/compute_scale.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/consolidate_metadata.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/create_query_data.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/create_single_dose_dataset.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_extreme_event.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_vars_crit_flag.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_joined.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_merged.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_param_bmi.md", "tests/testthat/_snaps/derive_param_bsa.md", "tests/testt